    <div class="space-y-4 text-justify">
  <p>
    Raffcomm Technologies Sdn. Bhd., widely known as RAFFTECH, is a trusted Certification Authority (CA) in Malaysia, licensed and regulated by the Malaysian Communications and Multimedia Commission (MCMC). RAFFTECH is authorized to provide verification and certification of entity, enhancing trust and integrity in digital processes, as well as online communications and transactions.
  </p>

  <p>
    Incorporated in 2010, RAFFTECH was awarded the operating license by MCMC in 2018 in compliance to the Digital Signature Act 1997 (DSA 1997), Digital Signature Regulations 1998 ("DSR 1998"), and Electronic Commerce Act 2006 (ECA 2006), for the provision of Certification Authority services, as well as recognized Repository and Date-Time Stamping services.
  </p>

  <p>
    RAFFTECH offers Digital Certificate for certification, and Digital Signature Solutions which is highly customizable to the client’s need. In its commitment to drive the adoption of Digital Signature, RAFFTECH collaborates with its strategic partner for the provision of Signing Cloud solution.
  </p>

  <p>
    Apart from being licensed as a CA, RAFFTECH has been appointed as the Authorised Service Provider for Suruhanjaya Syarikat Malaysia (SSM) in 2023. Prior to the appointment, RAFFTECH was already servicing SSM as CA for Digitally Certified True Copy (DCTC) documents.
  </p>

  <p>
    The appointment as Service Provider extends to overseeing the operation and enhancement of SSM E-Info portal, which was initially developed and managed by its holding company, Raffcomm Sdn Bhd (RAFFCOMM) since 2006.
  </p>

  <p>
    Leveraging the expertise and experience of the group, RAFFTECH aims to be the Prime Identity Services Company, providing secure authentication of corporate and individual information, making verified identification and cybersecurity universally accessible and reliable.
  </p>
</div>

